e by the National Certification Commission of Acupuncture and Oriental Medicine (NCCAOM). Denice has served as an instructor for five years at the Traditional Chinese College of Hawai‘i, teaching Clinical Acupuncture and Moxibustion, Traditional Diagnosis & Pathology and Chinese Pharmacology I & II. ","location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":19.619758,"lng":-155.94917,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"ff08abd9-b933-46c3-a734-9998abc7f2f6","name":"Doreen King","title":"$undefined","businessName":"Advanced Bodyworks","image":"https://ik.imagekit.io/mrys9mptj7/tr:w-768,h-768,cm-extract,x-74,y-0/Dr_King_Formal_Pic.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic, Nutrition, Acupuncture","modalities":["Chiropractic","Nutrition","Acupuncture"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Meet Dr. Doreen King of Advanced Bodyworks who contributes to providing quality service to our clients in Kamuela, HI.","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.021674,"lng":-155.675162,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"c287599f-2019-46d3-81a7-80ebcd0a2d88","name":"Craig Cain - Kiso Method","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic, Acupuncture, Massage, Alternative Therapy","modalities":["Chiropractic","Acupuncture","Massage","Alternative Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Find relief and healing at Awakening Healing Center in Hilo, Hawai'i. We offer chiropractic care, massage therapy, acupuncture, Vax-D, physical therapy, and veterans' services, all using the unique Kiso Method. Schedule your appointment today!","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.726014,"lng":-155.088223,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verif